OL,3,CChurch 'bucking the trend' as it
OL,4,Creopens after over a decade
OL,6,FIt is the church that opened twice.
OL,7,FOnce, in 1870 - and now, once again,
OL,8,Fin June 2024.
OL,10,FEven through its closure they held
OL,11,FChristmas and Easter and Epiphanies
OL,12,Fthere: the hymns were never entirely
OL,13,Funsung.
OL,15,FAnd so, as a decade - and slightly
OL,16,Fmore - passed - the argument to reopen
OL,17,Fit grew.
