OL,3,CChurch 'bucking the trend' as it
OL,4,Creopens after over a decade
OL,6,FVicar, the Rev Kevin Ellis, who has
OL,7,Fnine churches to balance in his very
OL,8,Flarge parish of Bro Madryn, said:
OL,9,F"It's the Friends' (of St Mary's)
OL,10,Fenthusiasm, and 'the willingness to
OL,11,Fhave a go' that made the argument.
OL,13,F"Then it's down to the Bishop to say
OL,14,Fyes. On Sunday, June the 9th, St
OL,15,FMary's had its grand reopening,
OL,16,Fcomplete with the Archbishop of Wales
OL,17,F- who also happens to be the Bishop of
OL,18,FBangor."
