OL,3,CChurch 'bucking the trend' as it
OL,4,Creopens after over a decade
OL,6,FThe first people to open St Mary's
OL,7,Fwore hats and had that Victorian
OL,8,Fcertainty that their church, the
OL,9,Fphysical building, would always be
OL,10,Fthere.
OL,12,FTheir 2024 counterparts have mobile
OL,13,Fphones and posted the reopening
OL,14,Fpictures on Facebook.
OL,16,FBut the faith and the sentiment
OL,17,Fhaven't changed, no matter how much we
OL,18,Fhave.
